The paper discusses the use of DUKPT for symmetric encryption key management in various mobile payment scenarios, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also addresses the applicability of DUKPT to cloud or remote wallet, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) aspects. The analysis of different use cases involves data communication (cs.DC) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
